2\\u20ac\\\" Kim Yeji (241.3) and Jin Ye Oh (243.2).The triumph has opened the country\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s account in the Paris Games and also ended a 12-year wait for its much-hyped shooters.\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"score\": 0.9910448407744752, \"rank\": 0.007536233748766089, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Korean_language\"}, {\"begin\": 337, \"end\": 340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.9997810452839835, \"rank\": 0.0001814463748764492, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 341, \"end\": 345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Itzy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2199011301512297e-13, \"text\": \"Yeji\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Itzy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Itzy\"}, {\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jin_Ye\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jin Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jin_Ye\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jin_Ye\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bhaker\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 244}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 287}, {\"ngram\": \"(243.2).The triumph\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 387}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s account\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"a 12-year wait\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 471}, {\"ngram\": \"its much-hyped shooters\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time India won shooting medals at the Olympics was in 2012 London edition where rapid-fire pistol shooter Vijay Kumar and 10m air rifle marksman Gagan Narang clinched silver and bronze respectively.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9987294755015594, \"rank\": 0.0010973706739602165, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999987303454, \"rank\": 1.2605444507840175e-09, \"text\": \"2012 London\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vijayakumar_(Tamil_actor)\", \"score\": 0.4890509893677375, \"rank\": 0.6427860696518394, \"text\": \"Vijay Kumar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vijayakumar_(Tamil_actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vijayakumar_(Tamil_actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 655, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gagan_Narang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gagan Narang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gagan_Narang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gagan_Narang\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shooting medals\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 540}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"10m\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Narang is the chef de mission of the Paris contingent right now.A Panjab University student Bhaker, who was competing in her second Olympics after drawing a blank in the previous edition, said, \\u00e2\\u20ac\\u0153After Tokyo, I was very disappointed and it took me a very long time to overcome that.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999547312665, \"rank\": 4.526858942994683e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 775, \"end\": 792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panjab_University\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.4420166667116224e-12, \"text\": \"Panjab University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panjab_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panjab_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Narang\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"the chef de mission\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"her second Olympics\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"a blank\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous edition\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"a very long time\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Frankly speaking, I really can not explain how good I am feeling today\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u00a6I was fighting with all the energy I have.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"today\\u00e2\\u20ac\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a6\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"all the energy\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Really grateful that I could win the bronze.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I read Bhagwat Gita and always tried to do what I am supposed to do, leaving everything else to god.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavad_Gita\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bhagwat Gita\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavad_Gita\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavad_Gita\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"god\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not fight destiny.\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u009dBhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s shooting story began in early 2016 when she took up the sport on her father Ramkishen Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s insistence at Universal Senior Secondary School in Goria, Jhajjar.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1449, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IIT_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.8682940825088106, \"rank\": 0.15168351205297187, \"text\": \"Jhajjar\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IIT_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IIT_Delhi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u2122s shooting story\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"Ramkishen Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s insistence\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"Universal Senior Secondary School\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"Goria\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In just one year, the Class XI girl became the national champion in all three categories \\u00e2\\u20ac\\\" youth, junior and women \\u00e2\\u20ac\\\" of the 10m air pistol event.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just o