\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The triumph has opened the country\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s account in the Paris Games and also ended a 12-year wait for its much-hyped shooters.\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The triumph\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3464}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s account\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3518}, {\"ngram\": \"a 12-year wait\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3548}, {\"ngram\": \"its much-hyped shooters\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time India won shooting medals at the Olympics was in 2012 London edition where rapid-fire pistol shooter Vijay Kumar and 10m air rifle marksman Gagan Narang clinched silver and bronze respectively.\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3592, \"end\": 3597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9987294755015594, \"rank\": 0.0010973706739602165, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 3641, \"end\": 3652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999987303454, \"rank\": 1.2605444507840175e-09, \"text\": \"2012 London\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3693, \"end\": 3704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vijayakumar_(Tamil_actor)\", \"score\": 0.4890509893677375, \"rank\": 0.6427860696518394, \"text\": \"Vijay Kumar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vijayakumar_(Tamil_actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vijayakumar_(Tamil_actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 3732, \"end\": 3744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gagan_Narang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gagan Narang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gagan_Narang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gagan_Narang\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shooting medals\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3617}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3633}, {\"ngram\": \"10m\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3712}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3760}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Narang is the chef de mission of the Paris contingent right now.\", \"from\": 3786, \"to\": 3850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3823, \"end\": 3828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999547312665, \"rank\": 4.526858942994683e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Narang\", \"from\": 3786, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"the chef de mission\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Panjab University student Bhaker, who was competing in her second Olympics after drawing a blank in the previous edition, said, \\u00e2\\u20ac\\u0153After Tokyo, I was very disappointed and it took me a very long time to overcome that.\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 4073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3856, \"end\": 3873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panjab_University\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.4420166667116224e-12, \"text\": \"Panjab University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panjab_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Panjab_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her second Olympics\", \"from\": 3911, \"to\": 3930}, {\"ngram\": \"a blank\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 3952}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous edition\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 3976}, {\"ngram\": \"a very long time\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Frankly speaking, I really can not explain how good I am feeling today\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u00a6I was fighting with all the energy I have.\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"today\\u00e2\\u20ac\", \"from\": 4139, \"to\": 4146}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a6\", \"from\": 4146, \"to\": 4147}, {\"ngram\": \"all the energy\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Really grateful that I could win the bronze.\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 4223, \"to\": 4233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I read Bhagwat Gita and always tried to do what I am supposed to do, leaving everything else to god.\", \"from\": 4235, \"to\": 4335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4242, \"end\": 4254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavad_Gita\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bhagwat Gita\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavad_Gita\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavad_Gita\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4312, \"to\": 4322}, {\"ngram\": \"god\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not fight destiny.\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u009d Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s shooting story began in early 2016 when she took up the sport on her father Ramkishen Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s insistence at Universal Senior Secondary School in Goria, Jhajjar.\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4534, \"end\": 4541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IIT_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.8682940825088106, \"rank\": 0.15168351205297187, \"text\": \"Jhajjar\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IIT_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IIT_Delhi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"destiny.\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u009d\", \"from\": 4353, \"to\": 4364}, {\"ngram\": \"Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s shooting story\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4390}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4428, \"to\": 4437}, {\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4451}, {\"ngram\": \"Ramkishen Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s insistence\", \"from\": 4452, \"to\": 4483}, {\"ngram\": \"Universal Senior Secondary School\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4520}, {\"ngram\": \"Goria\", \"from\": 4524, \"to\": 4529}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In just one year, the Class XI girl became the national champion in all three categories \\u00e2\\u20ac\\\" youth, junior and women \\u00e2\\u20ac\\\" of the 10m air pistol event.\", \"from\": 4543, \"to\": 4692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just one year\", \"from\": 4546, \"to\": 4559}, {\"ngram\": \"the Class XI girl\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4578}, {\"ngram\": \"the national champion\", \"from\": 4586, \"to\": 4607}, {\"ngram\": \"all three categories \\u00e2\\u20ac\\\" youth\", \"from\": 4611, \"to\": 4641}, {\"ngram\": \"junior and women \\u00e2\\u20ac\", \"from\": 4643, \"to\": 4662}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10m air pistol event\", \"from\": 4667, \"to\": 4691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just eight years after taking up the sport, the 2020 Arjuna awardee has an Olympics bronze.\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 4784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4746, \"end\": 4752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arjuna_Award\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2386682464420925e-20, \"text\": \"Arjuna\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arjuna_Award\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arjuna_Award\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4735}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics bronze\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CM Hails Bhaker for Winning Bronze Haryana Chief Minister Nayab Singh Saini on Sunday extended his heartfelt congratulations to Manu Bhaker for her outstanding achi