\": 4959}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 4972, \"to\": 4986}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10-meter air pistol event\", \"from\": 4990, \"to\": 5019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saini, in his message, lauded Bhaker for her remarkable performance and historical achievement, which has brought immense pride to both Haryana and the entire nation.\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5049, \"end\": 5054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Saini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\"}, {\"begin\": 5185, \"end\": 5192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900831681423928e-14, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his message\", \"from\": 5059, \"to\": 5070}, {\"ngram\": \"Bhaker\", \"from\": 5079, \"to\": 5085}, {\"ngram\": \"her remarkable performance\", \"from\": 5090, \"to\": 5116}, {\"ngram\": \"historical achievement\", \"from\": 5121, \"to\": 5143}, {\"ngram\": \"immense pride\", \"from\": 5163, \"to\": 5176}, {\"ngram\": \"the entire nation\", \"from\": 5197, \"to\": 5214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Praising her dedication, hard work, and perseverance that led to this prestigious accomplishment on the global stage, Saini said: \\u00e2\\u20ac\\u0153Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s success is a testament to her extraordinary talent and relentless effort.\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5337, \"end\": 5342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Saini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her dedication\", \"from\": 5228, \"to\": 5242}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 5244, \"to\": 5253}, {\"ngram\": \"perseverance\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5271}, {\"ngram\": \"this prestigious accomplishment\", \"from\": 5284, \"to\": 5315}, {\"ngram\": \"the global stage\", \"from\": 5319, \"to\": 5335}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u0153Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s success\", \"from\": 5349, \"to\": 5370}, {\"ngram\": \"a testament\", \"from\": 5374, \"to\": 5385}, {\"ngram\": \"her extraordinary talent and relentless effort\", \"from\": 5389, \"to\": 5435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has not only made Haryana proud but also set an inspiring example for aspiring athletes across the country\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u00a6We are confident that our players will continue to excel and bring more laurels to the state and the country.\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u009d Also congratulating all the athletes from Haryana participating in the ongoing Paris Olympics, the Chief Minister expressed his optimism that these athletes will continue to perform exceptionally well and secure more medals for India.\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5459, \"end\": 5466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900831681423928e-14, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 5708, \"end\": 5715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900831681423928e-14, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 5894, \"end\": 5899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9987294755015594, \"rank\": 0.0010973706739602165, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an i